Title: Blockchain-Based Supply Chain Transparency in the Food Industry
Authors: Dr. Robert Kim, Dr. Anna Petrova
Published: Supply Chain Management Review, 2024

Abstract:
We implement and evaluate a blockchain-based traceability system for food
supply chains spanning farm-to-table. Our pilot deployment across 3 major
grocery chains demonstrates 99.7% traceability accuracy and 40% reduction
in food recall response times.

Keywords: blockchain, supply chain, food safety, traceability
